value:
Nino's smile... There's no better
gift than that.

Wherever I went, all I saw were
bodies... Here, wherever I go, I
see smiles... Strange...

Here, nobody's afraid of me... How
can the Angel of Death be mobbed
by...kids?

When you hand somebody a present,
how should you look at them? Can
you...show me?

I could never assassinate someone
wearing these clothes... Then again,
I guess I don't need to right now...

Here... A gift, from
$Nf...

I have a gift that absolutely must
be delivered...

A festival? It doesn't matter... The
hunter must kill his prey without
fail...no matter when or where...
The chill dulls my senses...
For me? Thanks...

I am the Angel of Death, Jaffar. This...
is a winter festival? It looks a bit...
lively...for me...

Until now...I have lived my life by
taking the lives of others... I didn't
know any other way to survive.$k$pI am the Angel of Death... I never
thought about how to make anyone
smile before...$k$pThanks to the winter festival, I
learned that you can give as well
as take...$k$pI do not intend to atone for my sins,
but maybe tonight...I can lead a
different life...$k$pEver since I met you, my thoughts
have become restless. Hmph...
たあっ
行け！
ぐっ…
しくじったか…
Merciful night.
Take this!
This is a gift.
It ends tonight.
I feel...cold.
What now...?
I have never been to a winter festival. What am I supposed to do?
Nino forced me to wear this. Do I look as uncomfortable as I feel?
I'm the Angel of Death. Hardly suited to such a lively occasion.
At night, I try to relax. These bright lights are keeping me on edge.
Am I enjoying myself? No. I'm here because I have to be.
Being festive does not come easily to me. But as long as Nino is happy, I can't complain.
A present...for me? Huh. Thank you.
Got it.
Is that snow?
For you.
